snippet.title: That Which Gave Chase - FULL PLAY (Haunted Demo Disc 2021)
snippet.description:
Full play of the game That Which Gave Chase. With a storm on the horizon, a sled dog musher is hired to transport a strange scientist into the mountains. Created by Aslak @aaslakk

Did you like That Which Gave Chase or one of the other Haunted Demo Disc 2021 games?
